text: Kashi can mean: * Varanasi (Also known as Kāśi), a city in India * Kashi Company, U.S. manufacturer of natural foods such as breakfast cereal, crackers, and cereal bars * Kashgar (pinyin transliteration of the Chinese: Kashi), a city in Xinjiang, western China * Japanese white oak *Kashii, Japan, part of Fukuoka city
title: Kashi
